org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.fxg.dom

Class AbstractFXGNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.fxg.dom.AbstractFXGNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFXGNode
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractFillNode, AbstractFilterNode, AbstractRichTextNode, AbstractStrokeNode, AbstractTextNode, AbstractTransformNode, CDATANode, DefinitionNode, GradientEntryNode, GraphicContentNode, GraphicNode, GroupDefinitionNode, LibraryNode

    public abstract class AbstractFXGNode
extends Object
implements IFXGNode
    A helper class that serves as the base implementation of IFXGNode. Subclasses can delegate to this class to handle unknown attributes or children.
